item.title: That 80s Show | The Chippendales broke Paulo's algorithm | Sting dancing and Johnny 5's murderous cousin | The Chart Savant.
item.description:
After delving into Dori's Chippendale multi-media content, Paulo's algorithms think he's a mid-80s housewife.

We find out about Marty and Doc's reunion at NYC Comicon and it makes Dori sad. To cheer herself up she watched a Sting movie that should have starred Johnny Rotten. Fun day.

The Chart Savant joins us for his chart game and it gives Paulo a chance to display the finest sleuthing since Angela Lansbury rode into town with her typewriter... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/8af1880/podcast/rss
